                <pre id="readme" class="bg-gray-900 text-green-400 p-4 rounded-lg overflow-x-auto text-sm"><code># NIT Campuz Learning Management System

[![Django](https://img.shields.io/badge/Django-4.2+-green.svg)](https://www.djangoproject.com/)
[![Python](https://img.shields.io/badge/Python-3.9+-blue.svg)](https://www.python.org/)
[![PostgreSQL](https://img.shields.io/badge/PostgreSQL-13+-blue.svg)](https://www.postgresql.org/)
[![Redis](https://img.shields.io/badge/Redis-6+-red.svg)](https://redis.io/)
[![Docker](https://img.shields.io/badge/Docker-Ready-blue.svg)](https://www.docker.com/)

A comprehensive, production-ready Learning Management System built with Django 4.2+, designed specifically for NIT campuses and modern educational institutions.

## ğŸš€ Features

### ğŸ” Role-Based Access Control
- **ADMIN**: Full system control and management
- **PRINCIPAL**: Cross-department oversight and course approval
- **HOD**: Department management and staff assignment
- **STAFF**: Course material upload and grade management
- **STUDENT**: Course access, assignments, and progress tracking

### ğŸ“š Core Functionality
- **Course Management**: Three-tier hierarchy (Course â†’ Module â†’ Lesson)
- **Assessment System**: Internal marks, assignments, automated grading
- **Digital Library**: Searchable repository with role-based access
- **Media Handling**: Secure file serving and video streaming
- **Real-time Analytics**: Progress tracking and performance metrics
- **Security & Performance**: JWT authentication, rate limiting, Redis caching

## ğŸ› ï¸ Tech Stack

- **Backend**: Django 4.2+, Django REST Framework
- **Database**: PostgreSQL 13+
- **Cache**: Redis 6+
- **Storage**: AWS S3 (configurable)
- **Authentication**: JWT tokens
- **Containerization**: Docker & Docker Compose
- **Testing**: Pytest with 80%+ coverage

## ğŸ“‹ Prerequisites

- Python 3.9+
- Docker & Docker Compose (recommended)
- PostgreSQL 13+ (if not using Docker)
- Redis 6+ (if not using Docker)
- Git

## ğŸš€ Quick Start

### Method 1: Docker (Recommended)

